    <scopecontent id="aspace_6e4795c119e9614fbec11aacb6f9e6b4">
      <head>Scope and Content</head>
      <p>The collection consists of a ledger for the Adams Express Company recording shipments being
        moved from Hot Springs, Virginia, to Warm Springs, Virginia, between May and September of
        1912. The ledger tracks the date of receipt by the office, the origination, weight,
        consignee, destination, charges, and signature of recipient.</p>
    </scopecontent>
